title: AoK is done!
contentMarkdown:
My newest film, Acts of Kindness, is finally done. I've been working on this for the better part of last year. 
Starring Sagnik Mukherjee, Mouli Roy and Sayan Royan. Music by Abhirup Dutta. Shot by DP Titir Mukherjee.
Trailer will be dropping soon!

Cheers,
Sagnik
Aug 25'
